# FILE NAMING SYSTEM

The GoldenScript searches ONLY for numeric prefixes.

Examples:

```text
01.mp4
02.mp4
03 - wizard.mp4
04 - orbit.mp4
05 - UFO.mp4
```

ONLY the leading number matters.

This became one of the most important successful architecture changes.

