# FIRST SUCCESSFUL MPV IPC TEST

## Start MPV

```bash
mpv \
--idle=yes \
--fullscreen \
--keep-open=yes \
--input-ipc-server=/tmp/mpvsocket
```

## Test IPC

```bash
echo '{ "command": ["loadfile", "/path/to/video.mp4"] }' \
| socat - /tmp/mpvsocket
```

This validated:

* persistent mpv engine
* IPC control
* live clip loading

This was the birth of Pi-GATO architecture.

