---

# MAJOR ARCHITECTURAL DISCOVERIES

## 1. Persistent MPV Is Mandatory

Restarting mpv for every clip was unstable.

Correct solution:
ONE persistent mpv instance.

---

## 2. IPC Is The Core

Socket-driven playback became the heart of the system.

---

## 3. Launcher Must Exit

Multiple input readers caused catastrophic conflicts.

---

## 4. Audio Is Unnecessary

Removing audio massively increased system stability.

---

## 5. Filename Prefix Matching Is Superior

Matching:
01
02
03

instead of exact filenames allowed:

* easier file replacement
* human-readable names
* flexible banks

Huge usability improvement.

